{"tid":1303690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話時話梁振英仲有無日日喺度「恥與為伍」梗","createTime":"2019-07-10T11:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T11:59:44.000Z","uid":16365,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"737bf888e46ab42667279114c58a5edb86e6ef9d","tid":1303690,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢日鳩日喺度「恥與為伍」想斷蘋果米路<br />\n一來而蘋果真係多人睇，啲商戶唔會有好嘅宣傳途徑都唔用<br />\n二來人地開始行訂閱制，有班市民喺度幫補下<br />\n三來狼英facebook班fan屎全部藍絲廢老 又度縮又無消費力又無組織力啲錢留哂畀啲大媽<br />\n<br />\n結果屌你老尾網民一發功話抵制<br />\n個效果勁你千萬倍<br />\n放你幾條街 你個狼英尾燈又見唔到塵又食唔到仲日日喺度妹妹下喺度「恥與為伍」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一諗到將來個社會會慢慢將呢堆廢柴淘汰就好心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 梁振英你推動完香港民主運動之後已經無價值架啦，快啲收檔啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ce92590f8f6eaed04f9891791797da8c74c907","tid":1303690,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab492b488a63cc059447ac8433eaf61932fec59","tid":1303690,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmo